{"tid":1434834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Big Short 贏家話香港可能係下個金融危機既黑天鵝","createTime":"2019-08-09T01:36:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T01:50:36.000Z","uid":181281,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c02cd492348c9312b40a296938540bf46b2bba","tid":1434834,"uid":181281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:36:21.000Z","msg":"&lsquo;Big Short&rsquo;個Steve Eisman 成功預測到2008年金融風暴房地產市場會爆煲，然後就用CDS 去short d CDO/MBS。佢話金融危機往往係預計唔到既&rdquo;黑天鵝&rdquo;引起。黎緊既&rdquo;黑天鵝&rdquo;，好可能就係香港。<br />\n<br />\n如果政府繼續避開回應民眾既訴求，香港市民亦唔會讓步。繼續落去，對中美貿易談判同全球經濟絕對不利。<br />\n<br />\n結論係- 各位要繼續撐下去！我地要撐到國際市場都注意到香港，注意到中國就係一個濫權，漠視人權既國家，而香港既市民正為自由同人權奮戰！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2019/08/08/steve-eisman-says-hong-kong-protests-are-his-biggest-worry-with-economy-a-possible-black-swan.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2019%2F08%2F08%2Fsteve-eisman-says-hong-kong-protests-are-his-biggest-worry-with-economy-a-possible-black-swan.html&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=9bbbaf51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2019/08/08/steve-eisman-says-hong-kong-protests-are-his-biggest-worry-with-economy-a-possible-black-swan.html</a>"},{"pid":"23b2c25846d4312d081ad1f2e0137c642e0412dc","tid":1434834,"uid":297859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4c02cd492348c9312b40a296938540bf46b2bba","tid":1434834,"uid":181281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:36:21.000Z","msg":"&lsquo;Big Short&rsquo;個Steve Eisman 成功預測到2008年金融風暴房地產市場會爆煲，然後就用CDS 去short d CDO/MBS。佢話金融危機往往係預計唔到既&rdquo;黑天鵝&rdquo;引起。黎緊既&rdquo;黑天鵝&rdquo;，好可能就係香港。<br />\n<br />\n如果政府繼續避開回應民眾既訴求，香港市民亦唔會讓步。繼續落去，對中美貿易談判同全球經濟絕對不利。<br />\n<br />\n結論係- 各位要繼續撐下去！我地要撐到國際市場都注意到香港，注意到中國就係一個濫權，漠視人權既國家，而香港既市民正為自由同人權奮戰！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2019/08/08/steve-eisman-says-hong-kong-protests-are-his-biggest-worry-with-economy-a-possible-black-s